      Quite clever, really.<br /><br />As others have said, <a href="http://www.google.com/landing/2step/" class="postlink" rel="nofollow">make sure you enable two factor authentication on your Google account</a>. <br /><br />Yes, it might be a minor inconvenience for you occasionally; but imagine the inconvenience you'd suffer if you lost your account.
      
